&lt;p&gt;2.where can I find egg? toilet paper?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3.wheere are the shopping carts? 购物车&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;exturl&#34; data-url=&#34;aHR0cDovLzQuRG8=&#34;&gt;4.Do&lt;/span&gt; you need a bag? plastic/paper bag 塑料袋 / 纸袋&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5.Could you put this in a seperate bag? 单独装袋&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;6.Does it have a chip? 这个信用卡有没有芯片&lt;/p&gt;
